Umugabane w’'''Afurika''' ni umwe mu [[Umugabane w’Isi|migabane]] igize [[isi]].Ndetse ukaba umugabane wa kabiri m'[[ubunini]] ndetse no guturwa n'[[Abaturage Rusange|abaturage]] benshi ku isi nyuma ya [[Aziya]] <ref>http://igicumbi.com/index.php/ubukerarugendo-mu-rwanda/ibidukikije/item/550-afurika-ibihugu-binini-bigize-umugabane-wa-afurika</ref>. Afurika ifite [[ubuso]] bwa 30.3 million km<sup>2</sup>, ikaba igizwe n'ibihugu  54 (mirongo itanu na bitanu), ituwe n'abaturage bagera kuri [[Biliyali]] 1.3(2018). kandi ukikijwe n'i[[nyanja]] ya [[Atalantika]], iy'[[Ubuhinde]] ndetse n'iya [[Mediterane.]]

